epending on the severity and duration of abnormality.', 'Metabolism, Synergism', 'Caution is advised when trabectedin is prescribed with CYP450 3A4 inhibitors that are also potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/173213/', '', 'Tetracycline, Norfloxacin, Cefepime, Cefuroxime, Cefixime, Amikacin, Ofloxacin, Micafungin, Amphotericin B, Oteseconazole, Flucytosine, More', 'Topotecan, Teniposide', 1767369485);
